| `hooks/hooks.json` | Hook 路由配置（SessionStart/PreToolUse/Stop） |
| `hooks/pre-write-guard.sh` | 拦截 Orchestrator 直接修改业务代码 |
| `hooks/session-start.sh` | 注入 Orchestrator 规则到 Claude Code |
| `hooks/stop-guard.sh` | 阻止有未裁决分歧时退出 |

### Agent 定义
